OL,4,CCovid: Home-education numbers rise by
OL,5,C75%
OL,6, The number of children registering for
OL,7, home education in the UK rose by 75% in
OL,8, the first eight months of the current
OL,9, school year, according to BBC research.
OL,11,FIn north-west England numbers were 92%
OL,12,Fup on the previous two-year average,
OL,13,Ffigures from 153 councils show.
OL,15,FSome parents and councils - including
OL,16,Fin former hotspot Bolton - say the
OL,17,Fincrease is down to "Covid anxiety".
OL,19,FThe Department for Education says it
OL,20,Fsupports home-educating parents and
OL,21,Fplans to launch a registration system.
